title: LF Clash players (Silver/Gold)
body:
Cant find a team so i'm making one! Currently have a jungle and top, so need Mid/ADC/Sup.
Just dont be a toxic mofo and be willing to have a couple practice games! Even if youre jungle/top add me and send me a message and we may be able to swap roles.

replies.body:
I am a g3 top/sup main

Will add you in game
i'm keen and willing to play any role Gold 3 atm.
